org.sadun.util.xml
Interface PathMap

All Known Implementing Classes:
SimplePathMapCreatorHandler
public interface PathMap

An object that can be used to retrieve node values of an XML document via a path language. Note that the path language need not be as complex as XPath.

Version:
1.0
